-------- Knowledge Control Module for any ISO 92 compliant database This module controls the validity of the constraints of a Datastore and rejects the invalid records in an error table. It can be used for static controls as well as flow controls.
Restrictions: - Data cleansing can be performed only if an update key is defined on the controlled table.
Check this option if you want to drop and re-create the errors table. It can be useful if the structure of your target table has changed.
Check this option if you want to drop and re-create the table summarizing the errors.

create table <%=snpRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME","W")%> ( CATALOG_NAME <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , SCHEMA_NAME <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , RESOURCE_NAME <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, FULL_RES_NAME <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_TYPE <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "1", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_MESS <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , CHECK_DATE <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE", "", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ORIGIN <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_NAME <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "35", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_TYPE <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "2", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_COUNT <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "10", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> )

delete from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME", "W")%> where CATALOG_NAME = '<%=snpRef.getTargetTable("CATALOG")%>' and SCHEMA_NAME = '<%=snpRef.getTargetTable("SCHEMA")%>' and ORIGIN = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' and ERR_TYPE = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>'

create table <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( SESS_NO <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_NUMERIC", "10", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_TYPE <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "1", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_MESS <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CHECK_DATE <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE", "", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME] [DEST_CRE_DT] " + snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL"), ",\n\t", "", "")%>, ORIGIN <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_NAME <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "35", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_TYPE <%=snpRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "2", "")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> )

delete from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> where ((ERR_TYPE = 'S') and ('<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' = 'S')) or ((ERR_TYPE = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>') and (ORIGIN = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>'))

insert into <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( SESS_NO, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, ORIGIN, CHECK_DATE, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select <%=snpRef.getSession("SESS_NO")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=snpRef.getPK("MESS")%>', '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=snpRef.getPK("KEY_NAME")%>', 'PK', <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","CT_NAME","A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E where <%=snpRef.getColList("", snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]=E.[COL_NAME]", "
	and	", "", "PK=1")%> group by <%=snpRef.getColList("", "E.[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "PK")%> having count(*) > 1 ) <%=snpRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( SESS_NO, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, ORIGIN, CHECK_DATE, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select <%=snpRef.getSession("SESS_NO")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=snpRef.getAK("MESS")%>', '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=snpRef.getAK("KEY_NAME")%>', 'AK', <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","CT_NAME","A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E where <%=snpRef.getAKColList("", "(("+snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]=E.[COL_NAME]) or (("+snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] is null) and (E.[COL_NAME] is null)))", "
	and	", "")%> group by <%=snpRef.getAKColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "")%> having count(*) > 1 ) <%=snpRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( SESS_NO, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, CHECK_DATE, ORIGIN, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select <%=snpRef.getSession("SESS_NO")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=snpRef.getFK("MESS")%>', <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', '<%=snpRef.getFK("FK_NAME")%>', 'FK', <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> <%if (snpRef.getFK("COMPLEX_SQL").equals("")) {%> from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where not exists ( select 'x' from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "FK_PK_TABLE_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> PK where <%=snpRef.getFKColList("", snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] =PK.[PK_COL_NAME]", "
	and	", "")%> ) and <%=snpRef.getFKColList("",snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] is not null", "
and	", "")%> <%=snpRef.getFilter()%>
<%}else{%> from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=snpRef.getFK("FK_ALIAS")%> where not exists ( select 'x' from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "FK_PK_TABLE_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=snpRef.getFK("PK_ALIAS")%> where <%=snpRef.getFK("COMPLEX_SQL")%> ) <%=snpRef.getFilter()%> <%}%>

insert into <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( SESS_NO, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, CHECK_DATE, ORIGIN, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> ) select <%=snpRef.getSession("SESS_NO")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=snpRef.getCK("MESS")%>', <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', '<%=snpRef.getCK("COND_NAME")%>', 'CK', <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=snpRef.getCK("COND_ALIAS")%> where not (<%=snpRef.getCK("COND_SQL")%>) <%=snpRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( SESS_NO, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, CHECK_DATE, ORIGIN, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> ) select <%=snpRef.getSession("SESS_NO")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=snpRef.getNotNullCol("MESS")%>', <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', '<%=snpRef.getNotNullCol("COL_NAME")%>', 'NN', <%=snpRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP")%> from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> where <%=snpRef.getNotNullCol("COL_NAME")%> is null <%=snpRef.getFilter()%>

delete from <%=snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> <%=snpRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E <%if (snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE").equals("F")) {%> where (<%=snpRef.getColList("","(("+snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) OR ("+snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] is null AND E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "\n\tand \t", "", "UK=1")%>) <%}else{%> where (<%=snpRef.getColList("","(("+snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) OR ("+snpRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] is null AND E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "\n\tand \t", "", "PK=1")%>) <%}%> and (ERR_TYPE = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and SESS_NO = <%=snpRef.getSession("SESS_NO")%> and ORIGIN = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>') )
insert check sum into check table

insert into <%=snpRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME", "W")%> ( CATALOG_NAME, SCHEMA_NAME, RESOURCE_NAME, FULL_RES_NAME, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, CHECK_DATE, ORIGIN, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, ERR_COUNT ) select '<%=snpRef.getTargetTable("CATALOG")%>', '<%=snpRef.getTargetTable("SCHEMA")%>', '<%=snpRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_NAME")%>', '<%=snpRef.getTable("L","TARG_NAME","D")%>', E.ERR_TYPE, E.ERR_MESS, E.CHECK_DATE, E.ORIGIN, E.CONS_NAME, E.CONS_TYPE, count(*) from <%=snpRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> E where E.ERR_TYPE = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and E.ORIGIN = '<%=snpRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' group by E.ERR_TYPE, E.ERR_MESS, E.CHECK_DATE, E.ORIGIN, E.CONS_NAME, E.CONS_TYPE
